extendedInfo.description: Traditional Tic-tac-toe online game, it lies your pictures on a board of three by three competing against the machine, attacking or defending the chances of winning or losing the game, depending on your mental ability in the game. Choose your level of difficulty: Easy, medium or Hard. Change the button image: You can locate the image by default, a cute puppy, a direct image from your gallery or taken by a camera. Pleasant music and sounds for setting up your game.
